@startuml
title SIMPHERA Azure Deployment and Connectivity Sequence

actor "DevOps Engineer" as DevOps
participant "Terraform CLI" as Terraform
participant "Azure Resource Manager" as ARM
participant "Azure Key Vault" as KeyVault
participant "Virtual Network" as VNet
participant "AKS Cluster" as AKS
participant "PostgreSQL Flexible Server" as PostgreSQL
participant "Storage Account\n(MinIO)" as Storage
participant "Private Link" as PrivateLink
participant "License Server VM\n(Optional)" as LicenseVM
participant "Bastion Host\n(Optional)" as Bastion
participant "Log Analytics\n(Optional)" as LogAnalytics

DevOps -> Terraform: terraform init
activate Terraform
Terraform -> ARM: Initialize Azure Provider
activate ARM
ARM --> Terraform: Provider Ready
Terraform --> DevOps: Initialization Complete
deactivate Terraform

DevOps -> Terraform: terraform plan
activate Terraform
Terraform -> ARM: Request Resource Plan
ARM --> Terraform: Execution Plan
Terraform --> DevOps: Display Plan
deactivate Terraform

DevOps -> Terraform: terraform apply
activate Terraform

Terraform -> ARM: Create Resource Group
activate ARM
ARM --> Terraform: Resource Group Created
deactivate ARM

Terraform -> ARM: Deploy Virtual Network
activate ARM
ARM -> VNet: Create VNet with Subnets
activate VNet
note right of VNet
Subnets:
- AKS Subnet
- Execution Nodes
- GPU Nodes
- PaaS Services
- PostgreSQL Servers
- License Server
- Bastion Host
end note
VNet --> ARM: VNet Created
deactivate VNet
ARM --> Terraform: VNet Deployed
deactivate ARM

Terraform -> ARM: Deploy Azure Key Vault
activate ARM
ARM -> KeyVault: Create Key Vault
activate KeyVault
KeyVault --> ARM: Key Vault Created
ARM --> Terraform: Key Vault Deployed
deactivate ARM

Terraform -> KeyVault: Store Secrets
activate KeyVault
note right of KeyVault
Secrets:
- PostgreSQL Passwords
- License Server Credentials
- Encryption Keys
end note
KeyVault --> Terraform: Secrets Stored
deactivate KeyVault

Terraform -> ARM: Deploy AKS Cluster
activate ARM
ARM -> AKS: Create Kubernetes Cluster
activate AKS
note right of AKS
Configuration:
- Autoscaling Enabled
- Multiple Node Pools
- GPU-enabled Options
- Azure Policy Integration
end note
AKS -> VNet: Attach to AKS Subnet
VNet --> AKS: Subnet Attached
AKS --> ARM: AKS Cluster Created
deactivate AKS
ARM --> Terraform: AKS Deployed
deactivate ARM

Terraform -> ARM: Deploy PostgreSQL Flexible Servers
activate ARM
ARM -> PostgreSQL: Create PostgreSQL Servers
activate PostgreSQL
note right of PostgreSQL
Instances:
- Keycloak Database
- SIMPHERA Database
High Availability Enabled
end note
PostgreSQL -> VNet: Attach to PostgreSQL Subnet
VNet --> PostgreSQL: Subnet Attached
PostgreSQL --> ARM: PostgreSQL Servers Created
deactivate PostgreSQL
ARM --> Terraform: PostgreSQL Deployed
deactivate ARM

Terraform -> ARM: Deploy Storage Accounts
activate ARM
ARM -> Storage: Create Storage Accounts for MinIO
activate Storage
Storage -> VNet: Attach to PaaS Subnet
VNet --> Storage: Subnet Attached
Storage --> ARM: Storage Accounts Created
deactivate Storage
ARM --> Terraform: Storage Deployed
deactivate ARM

Terraform -> ARM: Configure Private Link
activate ARM
ARM -> PrivateLink: Create Private Endpoints
activate PrivateLink
PrivateLink -> PostgreSQL: Establish Private Connection
PostgreSQL --> PrivateLink: Connection Established
PrivateLink -> Storage: Establish Private Connection
Storage --> PrivateLink: Connection Established
PrivateLink -> VNet: Integrate with VNet
VNet --> PrivateLink: Integration Complete
PrivateLink --> ARM: Private Links Configured
deactivate PrivateLink
ARM --> Terraform: Private Link Deployed
deactivate ARM

opt Optional Components
    Terraform -> ARM: Deploy License Server VM
    activate ARM
    ARM -> LicenseVM: Create Windows VM
    activate LicenseVM
    LicenseVM -> VNet: Attach to License Server Subnet
    VNet --> LicenseVM: Subnet Attached
    LicenseVM -> KeyVault: Retrieve Disk Encryption Key
    KeyVault --> LicenseVM: Encryption Key Provided
    note right of LicenseVM
    Configuration:
    - dSPACE Installation Manager
    - IaaSAntimalware
    - MicrosoftMonitoringAgent
    end note
    LicenseVM --> ARM: License Server Created
    deactivate LicenseVM
    ARM --> Terraform: License Server Deployed
    deactivate ARM

    Terraform -> ARM: Deploy Bastion Host
    activate ARM
    ARM -> Bastion: Create Bastion Service
    activate Bastion
    Bastion -> VNet: Attach to Bastion Subnet
    VNet --> Bastion: Subnet Attached
    Bastion --> ARM: Bastion Created
    deactivate Bastion
    ARM --> Terraform: Bastion Deployed
    deactivate ARM

    Terraform -> ARM: Configure Log Analytics
    activate ARM
    ARM -> LogAnalytics: Create Log Analytics Workspace
    activate LogAnalytics
    LogAnalytics --> ARM: Workspace Created
    ARM --> Terraform: Log Analytics Deployed
    deactivate ARM

    Terraform -> AKS: Integrate with Log Analytics
    activate AKS
    AKS -> LogAnalytics: Send Logs and Metrics
    LogAnalytics --> AKS: Integration Confirmed
    deactivate LogAnalytics
    deactivate AKS
end

Terraform -> ARM: Apply Network Security Groups
activate ARM
ARM -> VNet: Configure NSGs on Subnets
VNet --> ARM: NSGs Applied
ARM --> Terraform: Security Configured
deactivate ARM

Terraform --> DevOps: Deployment Complete
deactivate Terraform

DevOps -> Terraform: terraform output
activate Terraform
Terraform --> DevOps: Output Values
note left of DevOps
Outputs:
- Kubeconfig
- PostgreSQL Hostnames
- Key Vault URI
- MinIO Endpoints
end note
deactivate Terraform

== Post-Deployment Connectivity ==

AKS -> PostgreSQL: Connect via Private Link
activate AKS
activate PostgreSQL
PostgreSQL --> AKS: Database Connection Established
deactivate PostgreSQL

AKS -> Storage: Access MinIO via Private Link
activate Storage
Storage --> AKS: Object Storage Connected
deactivate Storage

AKS -> KeyVault: Retrieve Secrets
activate KeyVault
KeyVault --> AKS: Secrets Provided
deactivate KeyVault
deactivate AKS

opt Bastion Access
    DevOps -> Bastion: Connect to Bastion
    activate Bastion
    Bastion -> LicenseVM: Secure SSH/RDP
    activate LicenseVM
    LicenseVM --> Bastion: Access Granted
    deactivate LicenseVM
    Bastion --> DevOps: Connected to VM
    deactivate Bastion
end

@enduml
